َ","translation":"pouring forth with a fragrance of musk. To that [wine of paradise], then, let all such aspire as [are willing to] aspire to things of high account:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5874.mp3","surahId":83,"words":[{"id":29131,"position":1,"arabic":"خِتَـٰمُهُۥ","translation":"তার মোহর (হবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/083_026_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29132,"position":2,"arabic":"مِسْكٌۭ ۚ","translation":"কস্তুরির","audioUrl":"wbw/083_026_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29134,"position":3,"arabic":"وَفِى","translation":"এবং ক্ষেত্রে","audioUrl":"wbw/083_026_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29135,"position":4,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এই","audioUrl":"wbw/083_026_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29136,"position":5,"arabic":"فَلْيَتَنَافَسِ","translation":"প্রতিযোগিতা করুক","audioUrl":"wbw/083_026_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29137,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْمُتَنَـٰفِسُونَ","translation":"প্রতিযোগীরা","audioUrl":"wbw/083_026_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29138,"position":7,"arabic":"٢٦","translation":"(২৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":27,"arabic":"وَمِزَاجُهُۥ مِن تَسْنِيمٍ","translation":"for it is composed of all that is most exalting","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5875.mp3","surahId":83,"words":[{"id":30018,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمِزَاجُهُۥ","translation":"এবং তার মিশ্রণ হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/083_027_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30019,"position":2,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"এর","audioUrl":"wbw/083_027_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30020,"position":3,"arabic":"تَسْنِيمٍ","translation":"তাসনীম","audioUrl":"wbw/083_027_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30021,"position":4,"arabic":"٢٧","translation":"(২৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":28,"arabic":"عَيْنًۭا يَشْرَبُ بِهَا ٱلْمُقَرَّبُونَ","translation":"a source [of bliss] whereof those who are drawn close unto God shall drink.","a